snippet.title: Fear And Loathing At The Border Patrol Checkpoint

localized.description:
We were 100 miles from the border when all of sudden....we entered a strange checkpoint. They wanted to know if we were citizens of the country we were in.... What an odd question we pondered.

  They descended on us like crazed goblins. Their gleaming beady eyes filled with visions of gleeful, tyrannical madness. 

  They asked, "Why..for the love of all that is the holy stasi state....why are YOU still chasing the American Dream?"
